          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Glorious, bright, and joyous, right and peaceful too;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why then like a wand’rer, roam with weary pace,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If the church of Jesus holds for you a place."
            }
          ]
